{%- comment -%}
  FAQPage JSON-LD with two sources:

  1. **Metafield-driven** (preferred): set `collection.metafields.seo.faqs` or
     `page.metafields.seo.faqs` in admin to a JSON list of {question, answer} objects.
     Any collection or page with the metafield set automatically gets schema.

     Metafield definition (one-time setup in Shopify admin → Settings → Custom data):
       Namespace + key: seo.faqs
       Type: JSON
       Example value:
         [
           {"question": "What metals do you use?", "answer": "Sterling silver and 14k gold."},
           {"question": "Do you ship internationally?", "answer": "Yes, to 30+ countries."}
         ]

  2. **Hardcoded fallback** for the Rose Thorn collection wedge (until the
     metafield is populated), so we ship working schema today.

  Eligible for FAQ rich result + AI Overview / Bing Copilot direct answers.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- liquid
  assign faqs_value = nil
  if request.page_type == 'collection' and collection.metafields.seo.faqs.value
    assign faqs_value = collection.metafields.seo.faqs.value
  elsif request.page_type == 'page' and page.metafields.seo.faqs.value
    assign faqs_value = page.metafields.seo.faqs.value
  endif
-%}

{%- if faqs_value and faqs_value.size > 0 -%}
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {%- for f in faqs_value -%}
          {
            "@type": "Question",
            "name": {{ f.question | json }},
            "acceptedAnswer": {
              "@type": "Answer",
              "text": {{ f.answer | json }}
            }
          }{%- unless forloop.last %},{% endunless -%}
        {%- endfor -%}
      ]
    }
  </script>
{%- elsif request.page_type == 'collection' and collection.handle == 'rose-thorn-collection' -%}
  {%- comment -%} Hardcoded fallback for the Rose Thorn wedge {%- endcomment -%}
  <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
      "@context": "https://schema.org",
      "@type": "FAQPage",
      "mainEntity": [
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What does thorn jewelry symbolize?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "In my work, the thorn represents protection and quiet strength — beauty that defends itself. Each Rose Thorn piece is sculpted by hand to be worn as a personal talisman."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What metals do you use for the Rose Thorn Collection?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Every Rose Thorn piece is available in sterling silver, with select pieces also offered in 14k rose gold and 14k yellow gold. Custom metals are available on request."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Are these pieces in stock and ready to ship?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes. The Rose Thorn Collection ships from my San Francisco studio within 3 to 5 business days. Custom finishes or commissions take longer — please contact me for a timeline."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "What is the price range for the Rose Thorn Collection?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Sterling silver pieces start at $85 for thorn studs and go up to $365 for the Rose Thorn Ring. Gold versions are priced higher; please see each product page for current pricing."
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Question",
          "name": "Can I commission a custom piece in the Rose Thorn style?",
          "acceptedAnswer": {
            "@type": "Answer",
            "text": "Yes. I love adapting the thorn motif into one-of-a-kind engagement rings, wedding bands, and heirloom pieces. Begin with a complimentary virtual consultation through the Custom Design Journey page."
          }
        }
      ]
    }
  </script>
{%- endif -%}
